PortSystem 1.0
name           gengetopt
version        2.9
categories     devel
maintainers    waqar@opendarwin.org
description    Generates a C function that uses getopt_long function
homepage       http://www.gnu.org/software/gengetopt/gengetopt.html
platforms      darwin
master_sites   ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/${name}/ \
               ftp://mirrors.kernel.org/gnu/${name}/ \
               http://mirrors.kernel.org/gnu/${name}/ \
               ftp://gatekeeper.dec.com/pub/GNU/${name}/ \
